			<div class="col-md-6">
				<h3>Punjab: Bhangra</h3>
				<p>Bhangra is a lively folk dance from Punjab, often performed
					during harvest festivals, weddings, and other joyous celebrations.
					The dance involves energetic movements accompanied by traditional
					drum beats (dhol). Bhangra has become internationally popular and
					is now performed in various parts of the world.</p>
