				<h3>Rajasthan: Ghoomar Dance</h3>
				<p>Ghoomar is a traditional Rajasthani folk dance performed by
					women, typically during festivals like Teej and Diwali. Dancers
					wear vibrant, flowing skirts and spin in circles while singing folk
					songs. It is a beautiful and graceful expression of Rajasthani
					culture.</p>
