				<h3>Kerala: Kathakali Dance</h3>
				<p>Kathakali is a classical dance-drama originating from Kerala,
					known for its elaborate costumes, vibrant makeup, and intricate
					storytelling. Performers use gestures and facial expressions to
					convey the story, which is usually based on Hindu mythology.</p>
			</div>
